custom_stopwords3 = dutch_stopwords| japanese_stopwords|italian_stopwords|hindi_stopwords
custom_stopwords4 = french_stopwords| spanish_stopwords|english_stopwords| modern_greek_stopwords
custom_stopwords5 = german_stopwords| bulgarian_stopwords| arabic_stopwords
custom_stopwords = custom_stopwords1 | custom_stopwords2 | custom_stopwords3| custom_stopwords4| custom_stopwords5
custom_stopwords = list(custom_stopwords)
custom_stopwords = [word.lower() for word in custom_stopwords]
custom_stopwords = [word for word in custom_stopwords if word.isalpha()]

In [866]:
pattern = re.compile(r'[!@#$(),\n"%^*?\:;~0-9\[\]]')

data_list = []
for text in X:
    text = pattern.sub(' ', text)
    text = text.lower().strip()
    data_list.append(text)
df['refined_text'] = data_list
X = df['refined_text']

In [1135]:
models = ['DecisionTreeClassifier', 'MultinomialNB', 'SVC']
train_scores = [train_d_c_ac, train_nb_c_ac, train_s_c_ac]
test_scores = [test_d_c_ac, test_nb_c_ac, test_s_c_ac]

x = np.arange(len(models))  
width = 0.35  

fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
bar1 = ax.bar(x - width/2, train_scores, width, label='Train accuracy', color='blue')
bar2 = ax.bar(x + width/2, test_scores, width, label='Test accuracy', color='orange')

ax.set_xlabel('Models')
ax.set_ylabel('Accuarcy')
ax.set_title('Accuracy Comparison: DecisionTreeClassifier vs MultinomialNB vs SVC \n')
ax.set_xticks(x)
ax.set_xticklabels(models)
ax.set_ylim(0, 1)  
ax.legend()

for bar in bar1 + bar2:
    height = bar.get_height()
    ax.annotate(f'{height:.3f}', xy=(bar.get_x() + bar.get_width() / 2, height),
                xytext=(0, 3), textcoords="offset points", ha='center', va='bottom')

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
